text: The Land (, translit. Al-ard) is a 1969 Egyptian drama movie directed by Youssef Chahine and was based on the novel by Abdel Rahman al-Sharqawi. It stars Hamdy Ahmed, Yehia Chahine, Ezzat El Alaili, Tewfik El Dekn, Mahmoud El- Meliguy. ==Other websites== * Category:1969 drama movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Youssef Chahine Category:Movies about landlords Category:Movies about farmers
